An American/USDM car for Season 2 would be great, possibly with something like a Fiero, fox body Mustang or a third gen Camaro/Firebird.

Another idea is to swap the parts and roles around, having a specific budget and doing all the beginner tuner mistakes there are: spending all the money on a more expensive car and having less money for parts (expensive car, cheap parts) and the other way around, having a cheap car but with expensive parts.
